Subject: Command to run genGitHtml and push to IPFS/IPNS
Message-Id: <c88858cc680dba11-0-artemis@nixos>

Run genGitHtml on a given repo, include a bare clone of the repo,
e.g. in a repo/ subdir, add a link to this bare repo to index.html, then
push to IPFS and publish to the repo's IPNS key.
